summary: An Ordinance ratifying the assignment from Seattle Yacht Club to the United States Shipping Board of a certain lease from The City of Seattle to that portion of Georgia Street and Georgia Street produced, in the City of Seattle, from the easterly line of Railroad Avenue to deep water in Elliott Bay, and also consenting to the assignment of said lease from the United States Shipping Board to the Navy Department of the United States.
committee: Streets & Sewers and Harbor & Public Grounds
